{"tid":1922751,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱返新工已經覺得要搵定後路","createTime":"2020-03-12T17:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T00:32:48.000Z","uid":345743,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a9aae582185383be4630163bdcc5480c429d4311","tid":1922751,"uid":345743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T17:44:47.000Z","msg":"其實1st in嗰時，大粒嗰個已經講咗好多次<br />\n「嗰條友主動遞信真係好，其實我已經想炒佢好耐」<br />\n「睇吓幾時炒埋其他人」<br />\n同埋不停數啲同事缺點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後2nd in大粒話「你做滿兩年，睇吓轉唔轉工囉」<br />\n我都懷疑，維唔維持到兩年<br />\n<br />\n而佢2nd in已經人身攻擊我<br />\n第一日返工再次兜口兜面人身攻擊<br />\n<br />\n我實在唔知佢份寫字樓工，係請人做嘢，定係請個人用來觀賞<br />\n亦唔知佢強調員工要「有禮貌」，係咪指下靶位畀佢踩三番四次，仍然對佢烚熟狗頭<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知會係我走先定佢炒先<br />\n唉冇專業技能真係好蝕底<br />\n睇吓公務員空缺先&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n呢份工經agent搵嘅<br />\n如果好似某fb page所講，agent真係會因應多位candidate嘅負評而blacklist employer<br />\n咁長遠而言<br />\n大粒佬成日都想炒人<br />\n炒多兩炒，搵多兩搵<br />\ncandidate負評畀agent知<br />\n以後係咪會小薯走晒，公司個朵臭晒，大粒佬經唔到agent請人？"},{"pid":"138d9469c51430d850893c6e09cf130d946323c3","tid":1922751,"uid":105121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T17:45:44.000Z","msg":"咁閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做咩嫁"},{"pid":"d1d32a7c03bc898009e2da0432c5a76134f2e542","tid":1922751,"uid":7020,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T17:46:17.000Z","msg":"點解佢人身攻擊你你都take offer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e73097426069a0c4401a58f291e588d692691f","tid":1922751,"uid":345743,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"138d9469c51430d850893c6e09cf130d946323c3","tid":1922751,"uid":105121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T17:45:44.000Z","msg":"咁閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做咩嫁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi